    "Giorgio Perfetti and his brother Augusto own candy and gum giant Perfetti Van Melle, a private company with more than $2.9 billion in revenues in 2022.",
    "His father Ambrogio and uncle Egidio started the company in 1946 as a chewing gum business in a small town near Milan.",
    "In 2022, the company announced it would acquire Mondelez International's developed market gum business, adding brands such as Trident, Dentyne and Bubbalicious.",
    "The company's top-selling brands include Mentos and Airheads."
  ],
